OL,4,CAfghan women to have rights within
OL,5,CIslamic law, Taliban says
OL,6, The rights of women in Afghanistan will
OL,7, be respected "within the framework of
OL,8, Islamic law", the Taliban say.
OL,10,FIn the group's first news conference
OL,11,Fsince taking control of the country on
OL,12,FSunday, a spokesman gave no details of
OL,13,Fwhat these freedoms would include.
OL,15,FZabihullah Mujahid simply repeated that
OL,16,FAfghans must live "within the framework
OL,17,Fof Islam".
OL,19,FHuman rights groups fear women's
OL,20,Ffreedoms could be eroded under the rule
OL,21,Fof the Islamists.
